{"tid":1577174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[戰爭]地理老師教路外國打支共必勝法","createTime":"2019-09-17T14:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:38:39.000Z","uid":174512,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"efc50c3466af1e3a6269eea39a0b8fafe6a35ab1","tid":1577174,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"記得以前地理老師成日笑外國唔識同中國打仗<br />\n打中國，只有三個字<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">炸水壩</span></span><br />\n講起水壩，小弟淨係識長江三峽天然彎曲果條<br />\n聽講呢條決堤嘅話，長江中下游所有城市（湖北、湖南、安徽、江西、浙江、江蘇、南京、<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上海</span></span>）幾億人民全部都要死<br />\n所有省市一夜覆沒<br />\n但原來...<br />\n中國有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.2萬</span></span>條最少超過15米嘅水壩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（wiki）最高果條305米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣炸一炸，分分鐘滅國都似<br />\n果幾十萬老解...可以幫手執屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n樓下實有啲仆街話中國人民無辜<br />\n咁太子站班手足就死有餘辜？<br />\nIf we burn,you burn with us呢句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你估講笑架？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱聽嘅就幫手推俾國際文宣手足睇<br />\n唔啱聽太殘忍嘅就由鳩佢沉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸於香港"},{"pid":"1aac53943d542040dcacbfab2d080704c7122ea1","tid":1577174,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"【極重要】（被？）自殺的失蹤人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0127bcf1677f69e0097d14e1b869d5d3c369a8eb","tid":1577174,"uid":174512,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"幾百支飛彈鳩射過去睇你擋到邊支"},{"pid":"4328559329c67d2addc17094d34cfee39264f515","tid":1577174,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:35:3